{"id": "art-244", "label": "Art. 244", "title": "Art. 244", "slug": "art-244", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 244 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1925799189\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1782\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1925799189\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Cu cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> o lun&#259; înainte de data adun&#259;rii\ngenerale extraordinare care urmeaz&#259; s&#259; se <span class=SpellE>pronun&#355;e</span>\nasupra proiectului de fuziune sau de divizare, organele de conducere ale <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> care iau parte la fuziune sau la\ndivizare vor pune la <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ia</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>/<span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>,\nla sediul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, urm&#259;toarele\ndocumente:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_603085646\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1781\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_603085646\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)proiectul de fuziune sau de divizare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1427323286\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1780\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1427323286\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)dac&#259; este cazul, raportul administratorilor\nprev&#259;zut la art. 243<sup>2</sup> alin. (1)-(3) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>/sau\ninformarea prev&#259;zut&#259; la art. 243<sup>2</sup> alin. (4);</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_891951714\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1779\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_891951714\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)<span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iile</span> financiare\nanuale <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> rapoartele de gestiune pentru ultimele\n3 <span class=SpellE>exerci&#355;ii</span> financiare ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\ncare iau parte la fuziune sau la divizare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_42010534\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1778\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_42010534\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)dac&#259; este cazul, <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iile</span>\nfinanciare, întocmite nu mai devreme de prima zi a celei de-a treia luni\nanterioare datei proiectului de fuziune sau de divizare, dac&#259; ultimele <span\nclass=SpellE>situa&#355;ii</span> financiare anuale au fost întocmite pentru un\n<span class=SpellE>exerci&#355;iu</span> financiar încheiat cu mai mult de 6\nluni înainte de aceast&#259; dat&#259;;</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1948620636\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1777\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1948620636\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)raportul cenzorilor sau, dup&#259; caz, raportul\nauditorului financiar;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_985560404\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1776\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_985560404\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)dac&#259; este cazul, raportul întocmit potrivit\nprevederilor art. 243<sup>3</sup>;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1357640597\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1775\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1357640597\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)<span class=SpellE>eviden&#355;a</span> contractelor cu\nvalori <span class=SpellE>dep&#259;&#351;ind</span> 10.000 lei fiecare <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> aflate în curs de executare, precum <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> repartizarea lor în caz de divizare a <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_325047249\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1774\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_325047249\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Întocmirea <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iilor</span>\nfinanciare prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) lit. d) nu este necesar&#259; dac&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> implicate în fuziune/divizare\npublic&#259; rapoarte semestriale <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> le pun la <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ia</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>/<span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>, potrivit <span class=SpellE>legisla&#355;iei</span>\n<span class=SpellE>pie&#355;ei</span> de capital, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nnici în cazul în care <span class=SpellE>to&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span>/<span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torii</span> de alte titluri care confer&#259;\ndrept de vot ai fiec&#259;reia dintre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nimplicate în fuziune/divizare au convenit astfel.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1042093119\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1773\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1042093119\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Societatea nu are <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;ia</span>\nde a pune la <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ia</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>\nla sediul s&#259;u social documentele prev&#259;zute la alin. (1), dac&#259;\nacestea sunt publicate pe propria pagin&#259; web a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\npe o perioad&#259; continu&#259; de cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> o\nlun&#259; înaintea adun&#259;rii generale care urmeaz&#259; s&#259; decid&#259;\ncu privire la fuziune/divizare, perioad&#259; care se încheie nu mai devreme de\nfinalul adun&#259;rii generale respective. <span class=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nart. 242 alin. (2<sup>2</sup>) se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1371185811\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1772\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1371185811\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)<span class=SpellE>Ac&#355;ionarii</span> sau <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> vor putea <span class=SpellE>ob&#355;ine</span>,\nla cerere <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> în mod gratuit, copii de pe actele\nenumerate la alin. (1) sau extrase din ele. În cazul în care un <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionar</span> sau asociat a fost de acord ca pentru\ncomunicarea de <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> societatea s&#259;\nutilizeze mijloace electronice, copii ale actelor prev&#259;zute la alin. (1)\nse pot transmite prin <span class=SpellE>po&#351;ta</span> electronic&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1161654153\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1771\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1161654153\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)<span class=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span> alin. (4) nu\nse aplic&#259; în cazul în care <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> sau <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> au posibilitatea de a desc&#259;rca de pe\npagina web a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nde a imprima documentele prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) pe întreaga perioad&#259;\nprev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (3).</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}